[[Casino Blitz Reward Cashier]] is a [[merchant]] who exchanges [[Casino Coin]]s for rewards in the [[Grand Sahil Casino]].

== Location ==
;[[Crystal Desert]]
* [[Crystal Oasis]]
** [[Free City of Amnoon]]
*** [[Grand Sahil Casino]]

