== Dialogue ==
:Welcome to the Grand Sahil! Are you here to trade in your casino coins from the [[Casino Blitz|blitz]] for other rewards?
:{{dialogue icon|more}} ''What blitz is that?''
::[[Zalambur|Our new owner]] is sponsoring a periodic competition to raise spirits and honor new visitors to [[Free City of Amnoon|Amnoon]] like yourself. During a blitz, casino coins are hidden in hard-to-reach locations throughout the city.
::{{dialogue icon|sell}} ''Can I see what you have to trade for those coins?''
::{{dialogue icon|end}} ''I see. Thanks for the information.''
:{{dialogue icon|sell}} ''Yes, I'm interested in trading.''
:{{dialogue icon|end}} ''Not just now, thanks.''

